{"tid":994070,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"港鐵荃灣線下半年轉用新信號系統　預告初期會有「陣痛」較多故障","createTime":"2019-01-24T11:43:26.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-25T09:54:17.000Z","uid":39464,"like":3,"dislike":32,"uniUserReply":36,"replies":[{"pid":"0c2962ad0a5fb89e70ef517ce954d0fbff4ed2d8","tid":994070,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-24T11:43:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20190124/s00001/f9f6e84aaa597bdfbab9958517f5f542.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20190124%2Fs00001%2Ff9f6e84aaa597bdfbab9958517f5f542.jpg&h=90697d72&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20190124/s00001/fa25356b99bebf2bcd9529a4471c37bd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20190124%2Fs00001%2Ffa25356b99bebf2bcd9529a4471c37bd.jpg&h=c3a17f1f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n港鐵今年下半年會在荃灣線轉用新信號系統，初期會以「雙系統」營運，即新舊系統一同使用。港鐵預告，轉用新系統初期會有「陣痛」，故障率或較高，會做好應變措施。<br />\n<br />\n港鐵車務總監劉天成表示，港鐵會逐一將列車轉為新系統，一旦發生故障，會停用相關列車。他說，按照經驗，轉用新系統初期會有較多故障，港鐵會做好應變措施，包括一旦出現服務延誤，會提供接駁巴士，及透過App向乘客廣播。<br />\n<br />\n此外，港鐵去年準點率為99.9%，全年有12宗延誤31分鐘或以上的事故，包括去年10月發生的四線故障（計算為4宗事故），罰款金額約2000萬元。<br />\n<br />\n高鐵方面，劉天成表示，2018年日均載客量5.2萬人次，認為數字屬「較好」，相信2019年會持續增長，但未有透露今年乘客量預測。今年農曆新年是高鐵香港段通車後首個「春運」，劉天成說，預計農曆新年期間，高鐵乘客量會與聖誕假期相若，本月31日（下周四）至下月11日，每日會增加13對列車往返西九總站及福田站，高峰期西九總站每日會增加100名人手。<br />\n<br />\n至於沙中線，港鐵表示，仍在研究會否分階段通車。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/港聞/article/20190124/s00001/1548325282839/【短片】港鐵荃灣線下半年轉用新信號系統-預告初期會有「陣痛」較多故障\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E%2Farticle%2F20190124%2Fs00001%2F1548325282839%2F%E3%80%90%E7%9F%AD%E7%89%87%E3%80%91%E6%B8%AF%E9%90%B5%E8%8D%83%E7%81%A3%E7%B7%9A%E4%B8%8B%E5%8D%8A%E5%B9%B4%E8%BD%89%E7%94%A8%E6%96%B0%E4%BF%A1%E8%99%9F%E7%B3%BB%E7%B5%B1-%E9%A0%90%E5%91%8A%E5%88%9D%E6%9C%9F%E6%9C%83%E6%9C%89%E3%80%8C%E9%99%A3%E7%97%9B%E3%80%8D%E8%BC%83%E5%A4%9A%E6%95%85%E9%9A%9C&d=jufLODGlwRth16sNQACzuQCO%2BKh2Nr2cOOQ8tL9eopA%3D&h=09a73473\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E%2Farticle%2F20190124%2Fs00001%2F1548325282839%2F%E3%80%90%E7%9F%AD%E7%89%87%E3%80%91%E6%B8%AF%E9%90%B5%E8%8D%83%E7%81%A3%E7%B7%9A%E4%B8%8B%E5%8D%8A%E5%B9%B4%E8%BD%89%E7%94%A8%E6%96%B0%E4%BF%A1%E8%99%9F%E7%B3%BB%E7%B5%B1-%E9%A0%90%E5%91%8A%E5%88%9D%E6%9C%9F%E6%9C%83%E6%9C%89%E3%80%8C%E9%99%A3%E7%97%9B%E3%80%8D%E8%BC%83%E5%A4%9A%E6%95%85%E9%9A%9C&h=618a8651\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/ins/港聞/article/20190124/s00001/1548325282839/【短片】港鐵荃灣線下半年轉用新信號系統-預告初期會有「陣痛」較多故障</a>"},{"pid":"d4fa10fd721c6e28ee4b5fda8993cb135d40180e","tid":994070,"uid":90820,"like":41,"dislike":1,"score":40,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-24T12:00:51.000Z","msg":"老細：港鐵上半年出咗新聞提你㗎啦，做乜唔凌晨出門口<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"494a8fb21ccb72d6577e215716f335f15b9be67d","tid":994070,"uid":17646,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-24T12:01:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e03b31702d4357a1dbc8ee77ccfdefd3186b4a09","tid":994070,"uid":64694,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-24T12:02:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e12c9fb561be84d91d34d303c54ae063c2d6ad74","tid":994070,"uid":90820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-24T12:11:28.000Z","msg":"以後要幾點起身返工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f09a428b0730f3ed66239dff2117805b7a0707f","tid":994070,"uid":7043,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-24T12:13:26.000Z","msg":"呀講撚到依家唔壞咁喎"},{"pid":"763f72dbb3806f5e32359cfd3c56aacd40f1e8c1","tid":994070,"uid":56698,"like":19,"dislike